maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Laser Moths.
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Лазерные мотыльки.
...Привет.

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Oh! So you've met those, too...
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Ох! Значит, что ты тоже с ними встретилась...

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Why?
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: За что?

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Why the Laser Moths?
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Почему лазерные мотыльки?

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Uhm... I don't know...
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Эмм... Я не знаю...

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: I want to strangle the person responsible for these enemies.
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Я хочу задушить человека, ответственного за этих врагов.

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Gosh...
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Боже...

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: By the way! The cold element is great, isn't it?
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Кстати! Элемент холода великолепен, не так ли?

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: [кивает]

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Uhm... Oui. I guess?
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Хмм... Oui (Да). Наверное?

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: You could almost say it is.\..\..\. cool!
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Можно даже сказать, что это так.\..\..\. свежо!

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: ...Oui.
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: ...Oui (Да).

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: A-Anyway... It's refreshing to have it in this hot environment.
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: В-Во всяком случае... Освежает в этой горячей обстановке.

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: To be honest, I was really craving some ice cream since we've been running through the desert.
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Честно говоря, я очень хотел мороженого, с тех пор, как мы бегали по пустыне.

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Oh~ Ice cream really would hit the spot right now!
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Ох~ Мороженое сейчас было бы действительно в тему!

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: It's too bad you can't just summon it with one of those cold skills.
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Жаль, что нельзя просто создать его каким-нибудь из холодных умений.

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Man, how strange would that be?
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Представь себе, как странно это выглядело бы?

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: I'd enjoy throwing ice cream at those laser moths and seeing them SUFFER!
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Я бы с удовольствием кидала мороженое в этих лазерных мотыльков и смотрела на их СТРАДАНИЯ!

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Gosh... you really do hate those moths, don't you?
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Господи... Ты действительно ненавидишь этих мотыльков?

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Very much. Anyway, let's wrap up this race.
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Очень сильно. В любом случае, пора заканчивать эту гонку.

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Yes! It shouldn't be much longer.
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Да! Это не должно занять много времени.

maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.orig: Bye!
maps/heat-dng/f4/corridor-east.json/enti.text: Пока!
